bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristid.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">25(43).50</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n115744.6\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> freq. in Prose, as a military term, of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">soldiers without heavy armour, light troops,</tr_> such as archers and slingers, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁπλῖται,</foreign> first in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:158\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.158</biblScope></bibl>, al., freq. in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author></bibl>, e. g. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁπλίζει τὸν δῆμον, πρότερον ψ. ὄντα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:27\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.27</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0074.tlg005:3:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Arr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tact.\">Tact.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.3</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ ψ. ὅμιλος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.125</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; so <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψιλοί</foreign> or <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ ψιλόν,</foreign> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ ὁπλιτικόν,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:2:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HG\">HG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.2.17</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg035.perseus-grc1:1321a:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pol.\">Pol.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1321a7</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψιλός,</foreign> opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὡπλισμένος,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1123\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">Aj.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1123</biblScope> </bibl>: coupled with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄσκευος,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:1029\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OC\">OC</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1029</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ψιλὸς στρατεύσομαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg008.perseus-grc1:232\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">232</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ψ. δύναμις</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg035.perseus-grc1:1321a:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\